        {
            "_id": "nPZlZs1rfnERketf",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Passive.webp",
            "name": "Undying Vendetta",
            "sort": 500000,
            "system": {
                "actionCategory": {
                    "value": "defensive"
                },
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "passive"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": null
                },
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>If the revenant's murderer dies, the revenant is immediately destroyed. A revenant that can't sense their murderer must attempt a @Check[type:flat|dc:11] check once every 24 hours to avoid becoming @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Immobilized]{Immobilized} and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Prone]{Prone}; they immediately rise again once they can sense their murderer. A murderer who becomes undead does not trigger the revenant's destruction until the murderer is finally destroyed. The revenant gains a +2 status bonus to checks and DCs against their murderer.</p>"
                },
